Release Process for pyLibravatar
================================

1. Bump the version number in `pyproject.toml`
2. Ensure all tests pass: `python -m pytest tests/`
3. Run pre-commit checks: `pre-commit run --all-files`
4. Install build tools: `pip install build twine`
5. Build the distribution: `python -m build`
6. Upload to PyPI: `twine upload dist/*`
7. Push the branch and create a git tag: `git push && git tag vX.Y.Z && git push --tags`
8. Create a GitHub release with release notes
